item.title: Help me on this varrock yew cutter....please....somebody good
item.dc:creator: @Westside_Rep Westside Rep
item.description:
@Westside_Rep wrote:

I made this and i didnt want to do it anymore… so somebody good do it… It takes you to the first yew tree and thats how far i got.

[code]program varrockweycutter;
{.include srl\srl.scar}
{.include srl\srl\skill\woodcutting.scar}
const
//-----Setup-----//
mmyewcolor =1214740;
mmstones =4802377;
//------End------//
procedure totrees;
begin
perfectnorth;
wait(500);
findmmcolor(x,y,mmstones)
movemousesmooth(x,y)
wait(500)
clickmouse(x,y,true)
wait(15000);
movemousesmooth(670,85)
wait(587);
clickmouse(670,85,true)
wait(5000)
MoveMouseSmooth(650,10)
Wait(645)
Clickmouse(650,10,true)
wait(16000);
movemouse(768, 175)
clickmouse(768, 175, true)
wait(7000);
findmmcolor(x,y,mmyewcolor)
movemouse (x,y)
wait(500);
clickmouse(x,y, true)
end;

begin
activateclient;
wait(1000);
totrees;
end.[/code]

if u do make it post it here first and at least give me some cred… I worked a while on this.
